> "\"There was a young man. I met him in the town. A few months ago now. We got to talking. Not about work. And I used my cover story, but he seemed to know it wasn't true. That got me wondering if he might be one of us.\"\n" [Continue]
> "Harris is not letting me off any more.\n" [Continue]
