    brink:  "\"It's a lonely life in this place,\" I reply. \"Lonely - and still one never gets a moment to oneself.\"\n"
  step 58: extra ("\"That's how it is in the Service,\" Harris answers.\n")
  step 59: extra ("\"I'm not in the Service.\"\n")
  step 60: extra ("Harris shakes his head. \"Yes, you are.\"\n")
  step 61: extra ("Then he waves the thought aside.\n")
  step 62: extra ("\"Go on with your confession.\"\n")
  step 63: extra ("That gives me pause. I hadn't thought of it as such. But I suppose he's right. I am about to admit what I did.\n")
  step 64: extra ("\"There's not much else to say. I took the part from Bombe computing device. You seem to know that already. I had to. He was going to expose me if I didn't.\"\n")
  step 65: extra ("\"This young man was blackmailing you over your affair?\"\n")

